Also note:<br>
<br>
If you give the 62 (rogue) water pet 2 swords/fists he will lose his ability to backstab.  Give him a Dagger of Symbols afterwards and his backstabs will return.<br>
<br>
This lowers the 62 pet's DPS slightly in comparison to the 61 pet, since it will lose it's mainhand proc.<br>
